{"tid":2317470,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劉家棟就蘇文隆重判一年案定罪及刑期上訴 將於12月18日高院聆訊","createTime":"2020-12-08T14:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T18:19:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6e451e7bf7620cc35fda454719b9bf6385c143a7","tid":2317470,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:58:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=196218175473035&amp;id=108296297598557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D196218175473035%26id%3D108296297598557&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3Wy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=9a07bd09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=196218175473035&amp;id=108296297598557</a><br />\n本人現被警方釋放，感激各界關心。<br />\n但仍有同事被拘留... 放心不下，繼續到警署等候消息。<br />\n<br />\n香港現在每天都是政治報復，今日還有八名民主派人士被捕，以及每天都有手足被判監。<br />\n<br />\n而我將於12月18日高等法院，對一年￼監禁及定罪進行上訴。若維持監禁刑罰，將會當天即時收監。<br />\n<br />\n我撐得住！香港人都要撐住！<br />\n<br />\n#這是當代香港人的命運<br />\n#也是當代香港人的責任"},{"pid":"9098c0dee2aa6ce5909e5dfc9dda64c8cd5a9da3","tid":2317470,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"69ce7ffd8aa17ba0e21fea93ea1dc60c4d38685d","tid":2317470,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9098c0dee2aa6ce5909e5dfc9dda64c8cd5a9da3","tid":2317470,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba19f9871dbb2e7ab388c2cf1312aaaf25861e7b","tid":2317470,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl